Package: mffield
Type: Package
Title: Classes, functions and methods for representing NWP fields
Version: 1.0
Date: 2024-04-08
Author: Harold Petithomme
Maintainer: <harold.petithomme@meteo.fr>
Description: Classes and functions for representing 2D and 3D NWP fields. Fields
 contain components for spatial and temporal representation. They can be observed,
 forecast or climatological fields. The spatial dimension is made of a horizontal
 component and a vertical axis.
License: no license
Depends: methods, parallel
Collate: TimeClass.R FcTimeClass.R DomainClass.R GridClass.R LAMGridClass.R
 GaussGridClass.R FieldClass.R ObsTimeClass.R fa.R
